direction: right

Telegram: User
Webhook: Server
BrainAPI: Server
MemoryEngine: Server
ShortMemory: Database
LongMemory: Filesystem
SearchEngine: Server
LLMProvider: External API
GeminiAPI: External API

User -> Webhook: Send Message (Text/Voice)
Webhook -> BrainAPI: Forward Update

BrainAPI -> MemoryEngine: processMessage(content)

MemoryEngine -> SearchEngine: search(content)
SearchEngine -> LLMProvider: generateEmbeddings(query)
LLMProvider -> GeminiAPI: Request Embeddings
GeminiAPI -> LLMProvider: Embeddings Vector
LLMProvider -> SearchEngine: Embeddings Vector
SearchEngine -> LongMemory: Retrieve relevant notes
LongMemory -> SearchEngine: Relevant Notes
SearchEngine -> MemoryEngine: Context (relevant notes summary)

MemoryEngine -> ShortMemory: getRecentMessages()
ShortMemory -> MemoryEngine: Conversation History

MemoryEngine -> LLMProvider: generateResponse(history, context)
LLMProvider -> GeminiAPI: Request Response
GeminiAPI -> LLMProvider: Response
LLMProvider -> MemoryEngine: LLM Response

MemoryEngine -> ShortMemory: addMessage(userMsg)
MemoryEngine -> ShortMemory: addMessage(assistantMsg)

MemoryEngine -> LLMProvider: classifyMemory(content)
LLMProvider -> GeminiAPI: Request Classification
GeminiAPI -> LLMProvider: Classification (YES/NO)
LLMProvider -> MemoryEngine: Classification Result

MemoryEngine -> LongMemory: saveNote(folder, note) (if YES)

MemoryEngine -> BrainAPI: Response Content
BrainAPI -> Webhook: Response Content
Webhook -> Telegram: Send Reply
Telegram -> User: Display Reply
